THE KEZIA ARCADE
Spontaneous and documentary in nature, The Kezia Arcade is a collection of photographs of people, places and details. The finished images are stylised and cinematic.

THE KEZIA LIBRARY
The Kezia Library is a collection of photographs taken over a lifetime by Kezia Barnett. The Kezia Arcade and Daily Photos are two collections within the Library.
Kezia is currently excavating these collections.

www.thekezialibrary.com

The artwork is authentic, created by, and copyright to artist Kezia Barnett. The purchase of this NFT is a purchase of the asset, not of the copyright.
